Flippio is a clean and Responsive Website Buy Sell Auction HTML Template Included 14 HTML files are well organized and named accordingly so it’s very easy to change any and all of the design. Our Template files are built with Bootstrap 4. Refine layout adapts to your needs and helps present your content in the most compelling way. You can customize it very easy to fit your Website Selling marketplace needs.

Key Features:

01 Home Pages.
13 Inner Pages.
Clean & Modern Design.
W3C Valid HTML5 & CSS.
Bootstrap v4
Fully responsive.
Responsive Dropdown Navigation.
Owl Carousel Used.
Smooth transition effects.
Cross Browser Optimization.
Free Updates.
Google font.
Standerd custom code Created.
All files are well commented.

Features Overview:

  • Responsive Layout Design:
    What ever you are using the device your site will run as it should be. This template is fully responsive layout for all type of devices.

  • Valid HTML Files :
    Flippio template coded with beautiful and clean codes! Some powerful HTML files 100% valid W3 web standards.

  • Awesome Blog Pages :
    Blogging very important! We designed beautiful blog page templates and single blog styles for your news and updates..

  • Bootstrap Framework:
    Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework for developing responsive, mobile first projects on the web.

Pages:

Template contains the following Pages:

  • Home
  • Websites
    • Websites
    • Website Details
  • Buying Process
  • Pages
    • All Webistes
    • Webistes Details
    • Buying Process
    • About
    • Pricing
    • Contact
    • Faq
    • Error page
    • Privacy
  • News
    • All News
    • News Details
  • Login
  • Signup

CSS and JavaScripts Libraries

Bootstrap v4
FontawesomeIcon
Jquery
Owl Carousel
Etc

What do you get?

All HTML files.
Documentation.
24/7 Support

Images Used

Pexels.
Freepik.
Unsplash.

Icon Used

FontAwesome

Note: Live preview images are not included in the final download. These are only for example purpose.

Support Facility:

Please send us your product presale query, after sales developer support request, customization project and any other queries to our dedicated support: software@thesoftking.com

Businex – React Corporate Business Template is a stunning website template designed for Business Agency, Corporate agency, Business Finance, Financing Investment service website.

Businex Corporate React template has a lot to give you. It comes with a total of 14+ pages where there are 2 unique Homepages. Businex is crafted with the assistance of Valid ReactJS, SCSS and Bootstrap 4.

Moreover, you will get Pixel Perfect Design, Sticky Header, Clean Markup and many more. Businex responsive template ensures the Cross-Browser compatibility, Parallax Effect and Responsive design.

Author and the visitors have the ultimate ease using this template. Font Awesome Icons, Well Documentation, Well Commented code, Easy Customization and Lifetime updates will potentially help you enjoy a better experience. Businex has a catchy look that attracts people at first site. The documentation service will surely help you build your site easily.

Download this template soon and renovate your business

Main Features List:

  • Build on React Platform (v16.12.0)
  • No jQuery Dependency
  • 2 Home Variations
  • 4 Blog Pages
  • Blog Grid/List View
  • Build with Bootstrap 4.x.x
  • Made with SASS
  • Font Awesome Icons
  • Google font include
  • Fully Responsive Design
  • W3C Validated Code
  • Clean Code
  • Speed Optimized
  • Cross Browser Support
  • Well Documented
  • No console error
  • Free Updates

IMAGES ARE NOT INCLUDED WITH THE DOWNLOADABLE FILE
